The detection mechanism is shown in Scheme 1
                        . The –COOH of R-CDs were inspired by EDC and NHS and bound with the –NH2 of aptamer to prepare selective near-infrared fluorescent carbon nanocomposites (R-CDs@apt). After adding Go to the system, because of the π-π stacking interaction with aptamer and Go, R-CDs@apt was adsorbed to the surface of Go (Fig. 3
                        ).
